OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1773360185
OL,3,C#2m of cannabis and 10 high-value
OL,4,Cvehicles seized after house raid
OL,6,FA man has been charged after #2million
OL,7,Fof cannabis was seized from a house in
OL,8,FLeeds.
OL,10,FPolice and immigration officials
OL,11,Farrested a man on suspicion of
OL,12,Ffraudulent document offences after
OL,13,Fraiding an address on Falkland Court,
OL,14,FMoortown.
OL,16,FA search led to the discovery of the
OL,17,F209 vacuum bags of dried cannabis,
OL,18,Fweighing about 1kg each and with an
OL,19,Festimated street value of #2.09m.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
