OL,3,C#2m of cannabis and 10 high-value
OL,4,Cvehicles seized after house raid
OL,6,FThe drugs, along with #30,000 in cash
OL,7,Fand 10 high-value vehicles have been
OL,8,Fseized.
OL,10,FRenat Sade, aged 32, of Falkland
OL,11,FCourt, has been charged with
OL,12,Fpossession of cannabis with intent to
OL,13,Fsupply, possession of criminal
OL,14,Fproperty and possession of a false
OL,15,Fidentity document with intent to
OL,16,Festablish personal information.
OL,18,FHe appeared before magistrates in
OL,19,FLeeds on Thursday and was remanded
OL,20,Finto custody to appear before Leeds
OL,21,FCrown Court on 9 April.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
